items.careInstruction:
-Use a PH Neutral Liquid detergent and avoid detergents containing bleaching or fluorescent brightening agents.
-Avoid using household washing machine or dryer. Wrap the item in a bath towel to remove moisture. Do not wring it like a cloth as it may damage the down, degrade its quality and cause features to poke through easily.
-Drip dry in a location away from direct sunlight. Do not store damp.
-This item has been treated with a water-repellent finish. The finish is not permanent. It will gradually wear off with cleaning and washing.
-Do not pull the down and feathers out. Pull them back in from the opposite side.
-Improper handling may accelerate deterioration.

Developed in conjunction with Toray Industries Textile innovation and technology specialists, Ultra Light Down is featherlight, water repellent and pocketable by design.
